init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Following the discovery, Soeurette invited all nations to a meeting in Las Vegas.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States was at a severe disadvantage and needed to catch up with the rest of the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She declared that the United States would embark on a campaign of global conquest to force all other nations into servitude.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: To lead the newly formed U.S. Empire, Soeurette appointed herself supreme ruler.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She appointed her ruthless brother, T.J. Morley, as the military commander and charged him with conquering all nations on Earth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She also appointed her daughter, Jayne Morley, as the commander of all spaceborne forces.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Campbell family was a long line of military leaders, and Harper followed suit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She then got word that the Campbell family had a history of mental illness.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette could not risk the possibility that Harper was insane.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette called upon the great doctors of her empire to help her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette reluctantly replaced Harper with her ex-husband, Dean Campbell.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette eventually gave up and let Tyler take the lead.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They would fight with each other and then make love, only to repeat the process over again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette eventually fell in love with Tyler all over again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She wanted to undo their divorce.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Tyler, however, had just started dating someone else.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She felt betrayed and let down by Tyler.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soeurette commandeered an army of tanks and stormed Tyler's abode.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Tyler's new girlfriend was crushed by one of the tanks.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Tyler retaliated and fired a rocket launcher at Soeurette, blasting her to pieces.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Tyler, as the new ruler of the U.S. Empire, had to deal with his ex-wife's demise.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He also immediately repealed all legislation that would have created a global dictatorship.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States increased its economic and military power quickly, thanks to the hard work of Tyler Campbell.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Tyler made the United States much stronger than it had been before.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world was finally at peace.
